                      "name": "desc",
                      "fill": "#71717A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Immerse yourself in the vibrant culture of Barcelona while studying at one of Spain's top-ranked universities. The Universitat de Barcelona offers a unique academic experience with courses available in both English and Spanish, allowing students to broaden their linguistic skills while pursuing their academic goals. Explore the rich history, art, and architecture of this Mediterranean city while earning transferable credits.",
