                      "fill": "#52525B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Experience the vibrant culture of Barcelona while earning academic credits at one of Spain's most prestigious universities. The Universitat de Barcelona offers a fully immersive study abroad experience that blends rigorous academics with cultural exploration. Students enroll directly in university courses alongside local and international peers, gaining a global perspective on their field of study. From the historic Gothic Quarter to the stunning beaches of Barceloneta, your classroom extends far beyond campus walls.",
